Title: Automating Patch Management and Package Updates at DataiTCloud

Introduction:

In this case study, we will explore the scenario where you, a newly hired DevOps engineer at DataiTCloud, 
are tasked with automating the patch management, package updates, and security patches for the Ubuntu platform used by the company. 
Currently, these tasks are performed manually every Friday. Your manager wants you to create a bash script and configure a cron job to automate this process, 
ensuring that it runs every hour, every day of the week throughout the year.


You have 10 minutes to do this
